name: 057 barre de fer
description:
"Sometimes I know exactly which scene I want to use in a movie. But to be honest, most of the time it's random. Here I grabbed the moment when Neo use an iron bar to fight the infinite Smiths. Impossible fight for him? This is a cool moment, I feel like when you have a very hard moment, a fight that become too hard, don't forget about the environment. Cause the environment builds the moment, in any way. hmmm I don't know where I go with this thought, now you have it. I want my NFTs to be some "mantra" or thoughts, I feel pure art for art is a bit of a waste of time hmmm don't u think ?"
